com.intel.jndn.utils.client

Class SegmentedFutureData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.jndn.utils.client.SegmentedFutureData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Future<net.named_data.jndn.Data>

    public class SegmentedFutureData
extends Object
implements Future<net.named_data.jndn.Data>
    Represents a list of Packets that have been requested asynchronously and have yet to be returned from the network. Usage: 
    
 SegmentedFutureData segmentedFutureData = new SegmentedFutureData(face, name, futureDataList);
 Data data = segmentedFutureData.get(); // will block until complete
    Author:
    Andrew Brown
